---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Capabilities & Engagements | Bright Horizon"
  description="Explore how Bright Horizon delivers digital transformation, cybersecurity, market opportunity facilitation, and IT enablement across Africa."
>

<!-- ── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="soft-gradient border-b border-[#1F7A63]/10">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/40 bg-[#C79C49]/10 px-4 py-1.5">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span>
        <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#6A4917]">Our Capabilities</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[#103B34] md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem]">
        Expertise that<br class="hidden sm:block" /> <span style="color: #c79c49;">drives outcomes.</span>
      </h1>
      <div class="mt-5 h-0.5 w-14 rounded-full" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.15));"></div>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/70">
        We don't offer generic solutions. Every engagement is scoped to your context — and measured by results you can point to. Here's where we operate and what we deliver.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── CAPABILITIES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
  <div class="mb-14 text-center">
    <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/30 bg-[#C79C49]/8 px-4 py-1.5">
      <span class="text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#6A4917]">Service Disciplines</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#103B34] md:text-4xl">Four disciplines. One integrated approach.</h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-xl text-base text-[#1A1A1A]/65">Our capabilities are interconnected — progress in one area strengthens the others.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">

    <!-- Digital Transformation -->
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,251,242,0.98) 0%, rgba(255,246,228,0.96) 100%); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -20px rgba(14,53,47,0.18);">
      <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.2));"></div>
      <div class="p-8">
        <div class="mb-5 flex items-start justify-between">
          <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(23,82,71,0.1), rgba(23,82,71,0.05)); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(23,82,71,0.1);">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#175247" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#c79c49]">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#103B34]">Digital Transformation</h3>
        <p class="mb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">We guide organisations through structured modernisation — from ERP implementation and systems integration to cloud-readiness programmes that align technology with strategy.</p>
        <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[#6A4917]">Typical engagements</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">ERP selection, configuration &amp; go-live support</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Legacy system modernisation roadmaps</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Cloud infrastructure planning &amp; migration</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Process automation and integration architecture</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Security & Compliance -->
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,251,242,0.98) 0%, rgba(255,246,228,0.96) 100%); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -20px rgba(14,53,47,0.18);">
      <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.2));"></div>
      <div class="p-8">
        <div class="mb-5 flex items-start justify-between">
          <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(23,82,71,0.1), rgba(23,82,71,0.05)); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(23,82,71,0.1);">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#175247" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#c79c49]">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#103B34]">Security &amp; Compliance</h3>
        <p class="mb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">We build cyber resilience into your operations — from identity governance and threat posture assessments to regulatory compliance aligned with POPIA and ISO standards.</p>
        <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[#6A4917]">Typical engagements</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Security posture assessment &amp; gap analysis</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">POPIA / ISO 27001 compliance readiness</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Identity &amp; access management frameworks</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Incident response planning &amp; cyber risk advisory</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Market Opportunity -->
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,251,242,0.98) 0%, rgba(255,246,228,0.96) 100%); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -20px rgba(14,53,47,0.18);">
      <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.2));"></div>
      <div class="p-8">
        <div class="mb-5 flex items-start justify-between">
          <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(23,82,71,0.1), rgba(23,82,71,0.05)); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(23,82,71,0.1);">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#175247" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#c79c49]">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#103B34]">Market Opportunity</h3>
        <p class="mb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">We connect organisations with the right partners, sectors, and entry points across African markets — with structured facilitation that reduces time-to-traction and de-risks expansion.</p>
        <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[#6A4917]">Typical engagements</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Pan-African market entry strategy &amp; facilitation</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Strategic partnership identification &amp; brokerage</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Cross-border opportunity analysis &amp; scoping</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Sector-specific introduction programmes</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- IT Enablement -->
    <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,251,242,0.98) 0%, rgba(255,246,228,0.96) 100%); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -20px rgba(14,53,47,0.18);">
      <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.2));"></div>
      <div class="p-8">
        <div class="mb-5 flex items-start justify-between">
          <div class="flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl border border-[#C79C49]/20" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(23,82,71,0.1), rgba(23,82,71,0.05)); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(23,82,71,0.1);">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#175247" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#c79c49]">04</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#103B34]">IT Enablement</h3>
        <p class="mb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">We build the operational technology foundation that lets your teams perform — through systems integration, managed support, and capability programmes aligned to your goals.</p>
        <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[#6A4917]">Typical engagements</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">IT infrastructure assessments &amp; planning</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Managed IT support &amp; service desk operations</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Systems integration &amp; API connectivity</p></div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-2.5"><span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span><p class="text-sm text-[#1A1A1A]/70">Staff capability building &amp; IT upskilling</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── ENGAGEMENT APPROACH ────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(160deg, #0f3c34 0%, #175247 55%, #1a6358 100%);">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="mb-14 text-center">
      <div class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/30 px-4 py-1.5" style="background: rgba(199,156,73,0.12);">
        <span class="text-[0.68rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#e1c178]">How We Engage</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#fffaf1] md:text-4xl">A structured path from brief to outcome.</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-xl text-base" style="color: rgba(255,244,222,0.6);">We don't improvise. Every engagement follows a deliberate process that keeps you informed and in control.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl" style="background: rgba(255,251,242,0.97); border: 1px solid rgba(199,156,73,0.22); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -20px rgba(10,35,31,0.45);">
        <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.25));"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="mb-3 text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#c79c49]">Step 01</p>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-extrabold text-[#103B34]">Assess</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">We start with a structured discovery session to understand your environment, goals, and constraints — before proposing anything.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl" style="background: rgba(255,251,242,0.97); border: 1px solid rgba(199,156,73,0.22); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -20px rgba(10,35,31,0.45);">
        <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.25));"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="mb-3 text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#c79c49]">Step 02</p>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-extrabold text-[#103B34]">Design</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">We co-create an engagement model tailored to your timeline, budget, and expected outcomes — with clear scope and no surprises.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl" style="background: rgba(255,251,242,0.97); border: 1px solid rgba(199,156,73,0.22); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -20px rgba(10,35,31,0.45);">
        <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.25));"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="mb-3 text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#c79c49]">Step 03</p>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-extrabold text-[#103B34]">Execute</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">Delivery is accountable and milestone-driven. We keep you informed at every stage and adapt quickly when circumstances change.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl" style="background: rgba(255,251,242,0.97); border: 1px solid rgba(199,156,73,0.22); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px -20px rgba(10,35,31,0.45);">
        <div class="h-1" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c79c49, rgba(199,156,73,0.25));"></div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="mb-3 text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[#c79c49]">Step 04</p>
          <h3 class="mb-2 text-lg font-extrabold text-[#103B34]">Sustain</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">Where relevant, we build in operational handover, ongoing support, and capability transfer so outcomes last beyond the engagement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── CTA ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-20">
  <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl" style="background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(23,82,71,0.06) 0%, rgba(255,250,241,0.98) 50%, rgba(199,156,73,0.1) 100%); border: 1px solid rgba(199,156,73,0.22); box-shadow: 0 24px 56px -28px rgba(14,53,47,0.2); padding: 4rem 3rem;">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center">
      <div class="mb-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#C79C49]/40 bg-[#C79C49]/10 px-4 py-1.5">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-[#c79c49]"></span>
        <span class="text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#6A4917]">Ready to engage?</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="max-w-2xl text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#103B34] md:text-4xl">Bring your brief. We'll handle the rest.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-[#1A1A1A]/65">Whether you have a clear requirement or just a challenge you need help framing — our first conversation is structured to give you clarity, not a sales pitch.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://dev.brighthorizon.co.za/contactus" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="btn-primary btn-shine inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-8 py-4 text-sm font-bold">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          Start the Conversation
        </a>
        <a href="https://cal.com/bright-horizon-apzin0/bright-horizon-consultation-requirements-use-case-discussion?overlayCalendar=true" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" class="consult-btn inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
          Book a Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</MainLayout>
